  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical study is to evaluate the effect of a four-week consumption of a
      fresh fermented dairy drink containing probiotic strains on Antibiotic-Associated Diarrhea
      and Gastro-Intestinal disorders in adult subjects treated for Helicobacter pylori
      eradication.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
